Pathway gene‐sets for PMMSq033

Source: R/genesets.R
genesets.Rd

A named list of gene sets used for hypergeometric enrichment tests in the PMMSq033 dataset.

Usage

genesets

Format

A named list of length length(genesets). Each element is a character vector of gene symbols corresponding to one pathway.

Source

Generated from extdata/PMMSq033/pathways.Rds via the data-raw/data.R preprocessing script.
